|u + v|^2 = (u + v) \cdot (u + v) = u \cdot u + 2u \cdot v + v \cdot v = \phi(u) \cdot \phi(u) + 2\phi(u) \cdot \phi(v) + \phi(v) \cdot \phi(v) = (\phi(u) + \phi(v)) \cdot (\phi(u) + \phi(v)) = |\phi(u) + \phi(v)|^2
